Package: ats-core
Version: 9.2.13-1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libssl3, zlib1g, libpcre3, libcap2, libhwloc15, libunwind8, libcurl4, tcl
Maintainer: ATS Proxy Enterprise <proxy@tripersonale.org>
Homepage: https://github.com/tripersonale/ats-proxy-enterprise
Description: Apache Traffic Server 9.2.13 LTS forward proxy core
 ATS 9.2.13 LTS compiled for Ubuntu 26.04, installed in /opt/trafficserver.
 Includes PCRE1 8.45 and default records.yaml configured as open forward proxy.
 This package provides the proxy engine without plugin or hardening.
